com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.component

Class Component

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.component.Component
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Entity
public class Component
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Entity class that modeling data base table Components. Contains queries, columns and relations to other tables. The purpose of the this table is to saves all the information for user created web components (name of the component and his type).
